        },
        {
            "id": "page5",
            "speaker": "birch",
            "lines": [
                "After hearing all that you've been up to, there is something I'd definitely like to share with you."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page6');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page6",
            "speaker": "birch",
            "lines": [
                "The fact of the matter is that after you resolved that kerfuffle with the super-ancient Pok\u00e9mon,"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page7');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page7",
            "speaker": "birch",
            "lines": [
