            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page9');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page9",
            "speaker": "birch",
            "lines": [
                "They are Pok\u00e9mon which are thought to have resided in Hoenn thousands of years ago!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page10');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page10",
            "speaker": "birch",
            "lines": [
                "We'll finally be able to meet Pok\u00e9mon never before seen, the very Pok\u00e9mon I've pursued all these years!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page11');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page11",
            "speaker": "birch",
            "lines": [
                "I'm so excited I feel like I'm about to burst!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page12');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page12",
            "speaker": "birch",
            "lines": [
                "So excited that I went right ahead and upgraded the Pok\u00e9dex to be ready for all of them!"
